g in the cafeteria food yesterday."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["Our supervisor got so peeved, man. He thinks having too much exciting food will distract us from our work."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["Now that Julie lady from one of the other rooms, she knew it was us, and boy was she furious."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["Gave me a big ol' lecture with some bigger words.\\.\\. Luckily, I didn't know what half of 'em meant."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["Anyway, I gotta run.\\.\\. Fast Skunk's new album just dropped."]},{"code":117,"indent":2,"parameters":[215]},{"code":0,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":402,"indent":1,"parameters":[2,"Entry #3"]},{"code":117,"indent":2,"parameters":[214]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["The following is an archived message from: [ERROR]"]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["Damnit Alex, we've been through this."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["We agreed by majority vote that our dorm's poster would be a Union Jack."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["Did you use our superglue this time or something? You know we're not allowed to use that outside of work!"]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["A have a Union Jack. C and D have the company's emblem. Don't bring up B as your excuse again... what they have as their poster is subhuman at best."]},{"code":101,"indent":2,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":2,"parameters":["How are we gonna get promoted like this??? You wanna be stuck here in C forever?"]},{"code":117,"indent":2,"parameters":[215]},{"code":0,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":402,"indent":1,"parameters":[3,"Exit"]},{"code":117,"indent":2,"parameters":[202]},{"code":113,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":2,"parameters":[]},{"code":404,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":413,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":1,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":0,"walkAnime":true}],"x":7,"y":3}
